ck box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 2 comments</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment byuser comment-author-admin even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-16573"> <article id="comment-16573" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/mia-foto-e1385566919652.jpg" width="1" height="1" alt="Giorgio Bagnoli" class="avatar avatar-75 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo" /></div><cite class="fn">Giorgio Bagnoli</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/tra-attrazione-e-sventura-rusalka-al-san-carlo-di-napoli/#comment-16573"><time datetime="2013-02-03T01:27:52+00:00">3 febbraio 2013 at 01:27</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Avvisiamo ancora una volta i lettori che siamo aperti a critiche intelligenti e motivate. Gli attacchi al solo scopo di offendere vengono immediatamente eliminati.</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-16586"> <article id="comment-16586" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b2f71df755c9ee2aa36fe3aad70bbf34?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Sabatino</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/tra-attrazione-e-sventura-rusalka-al-san-carlo-di-napoli/#comment-16586"><time datetime="2013-02-07T19:50:19+00:00">7 febbraio 2013 at 19:50</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Ero presente all&#8217;opera&#8230;non posso non dare Atto a ci che  scritto in questa recensione&#8230; riflessioni giuste&#8230; per quanto riguarda la scenografia&#8230;sulle voci nulla da dire&#8230;bravi tutti.<br /> Il tutto non ha dato impatto scenografico&#8230; L&#8217;orchestra scarsa di strumenti&#8230;anche se perfetta &#8230;direzione eccezionale. Complimenti a Francesca Di Giacomo per la recensione fatta.</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/01/tra-attrazione-e-sventura-rusalka-al-san-carlo-di-napoli/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_post_ID\' value=\'47188\' id=\'comment_post_ID\' /> <input 